Privacy Policy 

At AppleWaveTV, we take the privacy of our users very seriously. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose our users' personal information.

Information Collection

We do not collect personal information from our users unless they choose to voluntarily provide it to us. The information we may collect includes:

Non-personal information
Usage data
Use of Information

We use the information collected to provide and improve our services, as well as to communicate with our users. We may use the collected information to:

Provide updates and information about our services
Respond to user inquiries
Enhance the functionality and user-friendliness of our services
Prevent fraud and illegal activities
Information Disclosure

We do not sell, trade, or rent our users' personal information to third parties. However, we may disclose personal information:

In accordance with the law or in response to a legal request
To protect our rights, property, or safety, as well as those of our users
In connection with a merger, acquisition, or other corporate transaction
Xtream Codes Collection

Our application is designed to generate Xtream codes for collectors only. We do not guarantee the validity of the generated codes and we are not responsible for their use. Users are responsible for verifying the validity of the codes before using them.

Policy Changes

We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page and will take effect immediately upon posting. We encourage our users to regularly check this page to stay informed about our privacy practices.

Contact

If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at [medsa576@gmail.com]
